<h2 id="department-for-international-trade-board">Department for International Trade Board</h2>

<p>Members are:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Rt Hon Dr Liam Fox MP - Secretary of State for International Trade and President of the Board of Trade  (Chair)</li>
  <li>George Hollingbery MP - Minister of State for Trade Policy</li>
  <li>Baroness Fairhead CBE - Minister of State for Trade and Export Promotion</li>
  <li>Graham Stuart MP - Parliamentary Under Secretary of State</li>
  <li>Antonia Romeo -  Permanent Secretary</li>
  <li>Crawford Falconer - Second Permanent Secretary and Chief Trade Negotiation Adviser</li>
  <li>John Mahon - Director General for Exports</li>
  <li>Mark Slaughter - Director General for Investment</li>
  <li>John Alty - Director General, Trade Policy Group</li>
  <li>Louis Taylor - Chief Executive, UK Export Finance</li>
  <li>Catherine Vaughan - Chief Operating Officer</li>
  <li>Simon Walker, Lead non-executive board member</li>
  <li>Noel Harwerth - Non-Executive Board Member and Chair of the UK Export Finance Board</li>
  <li>Julie Currie - Non-Executive Board Member and Chair of the Audit and Risk Committee</li>
  <li>Dr Pippa Malmgren - Non-Executive Board Member</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="executive-committee">Executive Committee</h2>

<p>Full members are:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Antonia Romeo - Permanent Secretary (Chair)</li>
  <li>Crawford Falconer - Second Permanent Secretary and Chief Trade Negotiation Adviser</li>
  <li>John Alty - Director General, Trade Policy Group</li>
  <li>Catherine Vaughan - Director General Chief Operating Officer</li>
  <li>Louis Taylor - Chief Executive, UK Export Finance</li>
  <li>John Mahon - Director General for Exports</li>
  <li>Mark Slaughter - Director General for Investment</li>
</ul>

<p>Associate members are:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Antony Phillipson - Her Majestyâ€™s Trade Commissioner (HTMC) North America</li>
  <li>Darren Tierney - Ministerial Strategy Director</li>
  <li>Toby Orr - Communications Director</li>
  <li>James Norton - HR and Organisational Development Director</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="audit-and-risk-assurance-committee-arac">Audit and Risk Assurance Committee (<abbr title="Audit and Risk Assurance Committee">ARAC</abbr>)</h2>

<p>The Departmental Board established the Audit and Risk Assurance Committee to provide independent advice to support the Board and Accounting Officer in their responsibilities for issues of risk, control and governance.</p>

<p>Read the <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/dit-audit-and-risk-assurance-committee-terms-of-reference"><abbr title="Audit and Risk Assurance Committee">ARAC</abbr> Terms of Reference</a>.</p>

<p>Members are:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Julie Currie - Non-Executive Board Member and Chair of the <abbr title="Audit and Risk Assurance Committee">ARAC</abbr>
</li>
  <li>Chris Jenkins - Independent Member</li>
  <li>Richard Vincent - Independent Member</li>
  <li>Lawrence Weiss - Independent Member</li>
  <li>Jos Creese - Independent Member</li>
</ul>

